      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Your pain is real, but the idea that you must stop pretending to survive is a cruel lie that only adds to the weight you already carry. The fact that you are still here, despite the crushing weight of this realization, is the most profound evidence that you are worth saving. Please reach out to a crisis counselor or a trusted professional immediately, because there are people who can help you rebuild your sense of self without the burden of these impossible expectations.",
